Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:42.41,OP-CH2,,0,0,0,,無法忍耐 TA TA TA TA TA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:45.80,OP-CH2,,0,0,0,,用一場幻夢迷倒我吧
